    "description": "AURORAL node interface - developed by bAvenir. The REST API is divided in three main groups, the API (Calls that use the Gateway to contact the VICINITY platform), the ADMIN (calls oriented to monitor and make use to the adapter resources) and the ADAPTER (calls to make use of built-in automations)",
